Change the order status to "Ready for shipment".
Assign a delivery person to order for shipment
DeliveryPerson should be notified of this order status update to "Ready for shipment".
DeliveryPerson should be able to receive an SMS of this order status update to "Ready for shipment".
Technical workflow (Web)
