Menu Options for Customer Application
Update Profile - Redirect to update profile screen where customer can update his details i.e. Name, Mobile, Email.
Update Address - Redirect to update address screnn where customer can update his current address
Favourite Shops - Redirect to Favourite shops screen where shops marked as Favourite will be listed
My cart - Redirect to My Cart screen where Products present in Cart will be displayed
My Orders - All the Orders placed by the customer will be displayed
Track my recent order - Will display the latest status of the most recent order placed by the customer
My addresses - Redirect to My addresses screen where customer can update his alternate delivery addresses
Rate app  - Redirect to play store
Share App - Display the list of Social media where app could be shared
Contact Us - Redirect to contact us page
Exit Application - Exits the application

Requirement
Customer should be able to view and update his profile information.
Customer should be able to view and update his current address information.
Customer should be able to view the list of Shops marked as Favroite by the customer.
Customer should be able to see the items present in Cart organised by Shops.
Customer should be able to see all the Orders placed by Customer till date.
Customer should be able to see status of most recently placed order by customer.
Customer should be able to view and update the Delivery Addresses.
Customer should be able to add a new Delivery Addresses.


